data.title: Caesar And Cleopatra film (1945)
data.meta_description: Basil Sydney, Vivien Leigh & Claude Rains  Characters: Rufio, Cleopatra, Julius Caesar Film: Caesar And Cleopatra (1947)  Director: Gabriel Pascal 11 December 1945  1945: Vivien Leigh (1913-1967) as Cleopatra, Basil Sydney (1894-1968) as Rufio, and Claude Rains (1889-1967) as Julius Caesar, in the Two Cities/Rank film adaptation of Bernard Shaw's play 'Caesar And Cleopatra', directed by Gabriel Pascal. (Photo by Wilfrid Newton)     Date: 11-Dec-1945

Elevator Girl (2010)

Ryan Merriman & Lacey Chabert Characters: Jonathan, Libby Film: Elevator Girl (2010) Director: Bradford May 13 February 2010 Lacey Chabert and Ryan Merriman as free spirited Liberty Taylor and uptight Jonathan MacIntyre, a pair of opposites who get stuck in an elevator together only to discover that fate may be the one with its finger on the door button. Photo: Justin Lubin/2009 Crown Media Date: 13 February 2010
